    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="970005063">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-970005063" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-970005063" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="970005063">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuyanjun/">小愚先声</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-10-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">今年看到的最棒的一本书，谈美与生命，谈《桃花源记》，谈《长恨歌》，虽然有人觉得他考据不严谨，望文生义，但我还是多次收获满满的感动，就如蒋勋在书中说的：有些事不在于你知不知道，而在于你相不相信。在历史与诗歌之间，我选择后者。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="458858760">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-458858760" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-458858760" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="458858760">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Thomas.Xie/">蝉</a>
                    <span>2014-04-06</span>
